  "title": "Junior sales associate",
  "description": "<p>Junior Sales Associate!!!!</p><p><br />Job Description:</p><p>We are looking for motivated and customer-friendly individuals to join our team as Junior Sales Associates. In this role, you will support the sales team, assist customers, and help maintain a positive shopping or service experience. This is an entry-level position ideal for those looking to start a career in sales.<br /></p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><ul><li>﻿﻿Greet and assist customers with questions and product information</li><li>﻿﻿Process sales transactions (training provided)</li><li>﻿﻿Maintain cleanliness and organization in the sales<br />area</li><li>﻿﻿Learn product knowledge to better assist customers</li></ul><p><br />Requirements:</p><ul><li>﻿﻿Good communication and people skills</li><li>﻿﻿Friendly, approachable, and willing to learn</li><li>﻿﻿Ability to work in a fast-paced environment</li><li>﻿﻿Reliable, punctual, and responsible</li></ul>",
